Tool Used: Canva (canva.com)

This folder contains the Digital Literacy Awareness Infographic 
created for Task 1.

The infographic covers four topics:
1. What is Digital Literacy
2. Stay Safe Online
3. Build Your Digital Identity
4. Professional Email Etiquette

The design uses a dark blue theme with 3D icons to make the 
information visually engaging and easy to read at a glance.
The infographic is intended to be shared with batchmates as 
part of the Student Digital Ambassador role.
